	"system": {
		"description": "<p>When you choose this archetype at 3rd level you gain proficiency with Performance and with painter’s supplies. If you are already proficient in Performance, you gain an expertise die instead. Additionally, you learn the @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.kh26gom04osoo005]{Dancing Lights} and @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.4oruofw2q7gso9hq]{Minor Illusion} cantrips, and they do not count against your maximum cantrips known. You also add the <em>prismatic</em> and <em>illusion</em> schools of magic to your list of bard spells.</p>",
